column1: TABLE D-4c. SUMMARY OF SELECTED ACUTE AQUATIC HABITAT GOALS
1. Refer to Table D-4d and D-4e for summary of aquatic habitat goal sources.  Used for selection of groundwater action levels.
2. Estuarine Goal = Lowest of Freshwater vs Saltwater chronic goals.
3. Drinking water goal substituted as aquatic habitat goal if latter was not available (see text).
